wi_steps.step_desc: 2) Unscrew these 2 screws and remove the item from the components.
3) Unscrew these 2 screws, and pull the pillars and the holder apart.
4) Prepare all 4 wheels, both front and rear.
5) Unscrew this screw and remove all the small items.

6) Find this screw and unscrew it, make sure that you hold the CV joint when unscrewing.
7) Separate all the components.
8) Remove the tyre from the rim.

9) Prepare the rim protector.
10) Notice that the rim has an edge that pops out, the opposite of it should go into the rim protector.

11) Place the rim into the rim protector by pushing it down.
12) Repeat the steps for wheel disassembly for the other 3 wheels.
